{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436094539,"sessionID":"ses_316fcbbc9ffe0U7d2IN0Q9PcrR","part":{"id":"prt_ce9073c870012EO8R1LkTQtLJu","sessionID":"ses_316fcbbc9ffe0U7d2IN0Q9PcrR","messageID":"msg_ce907332a001Irbm5kTvZHG2vA","type":"text","text":"The `logs.ts`, `abort.ts`, and `graph.ts` commands already use `output()` but they don't have specific TOON formats in the spec. The generic fallback in `output()` will handle them. These commands can get TOON output via the generic renderer without needing specific TOON renderers.\n\nLet me now run typecheck and build:","time":{"start":1773436094539,"end":1773436094539}}}
